This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4604

This plugin contains indent and syntax plugins for Balsa.
Balsa is an asynchronous circuit synthesis system and hardware description language.
To get more information, visit http://apt.cs.manchester.ac.uk/projects/tools/balsa/

For more detail see also project page https://github.com/qeexee/balsa-vim
